documentation.text:
@dev buy function when the nft is in sale
 @param _tokenId The ID of the NFT

devdoc.author: Germain Winckel
devdoc.details: The blockCar contract which inherits from ERC721

Approval(address,address,uint256).details: Emitted when `owner` enables `approved` to manage the `tokenId` token.

ApprovalForAll(address,address,bool).details: Emitted when `owner` enables or disables (`approved`) `operator` to manage all of its assets.

ChangingStatus(string,address,uint256,ui.details: An event when a car is for sale

LogDepositReceived(address).details: An event when a deposit is received

Minted(address,string,uint256,string,str.details: An event that registers when a user did the KYC for a car

Transfer(address,address,uint256).details: Emitted when `tokenId` token is transferred from `from` to `to`.

addDocumentLink(string,uint256).details: add a link to linkDocument in the same field. The separator is ";"

askKyc(uint256).details: Change boolean 'isWaitingKyc' to false, the admnin has to approve now

buyNftAndTransferValue(uint256).details: buy function when the nft is in sale

carFound(uint256).details: Change boolean 'isStolen' to true, the car was found

carIsForSale(uint256,uint32,uint32,strin.details: Change boolean 'isOnSale' to true, this car is for sale

carIsScrapped(uint256).details: Change boolean 'isScrapped' to true, this car is Scrapped

carIsStolen(uint256).details: Change boolean 'isStolen' to true, this car is stolen

delegeteCar(address,uint256).details: Change boolean 'isDelegated' to true, this car is Delegated

getCurrentId().details: Returns the current value of the tokenIds counter, which represents the number of tokens minted so far.

returns._0: current value of the tokenIds counter.

getNftIdsByAddress(address).details: Returns an array of NFT IDs owned by the specified address.

params._owner: The address to retrieve NFT IDs for.

getNftIdsByDelegatorAddress(address).details: Returns an array of NFT IDs owned by a delelegator address.

params._owner: The address to retrieve NFT IDs for.

getNftIdsByOnSale().details: Returns an array of NFT of all NFT which have status isOnSale to true

kycIsApproved(uint256).details: Change the status of isKycDone to true, so the KYC is done

params._power: : Power of the car in Kw

returns._0: newItemId The Id of the NFT

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

stopDelegation(uint256).details: Change boolean 'isDelegated' to false, this car is not delegated anymore

stopSale(uint256).details: Change boolean 'isOnSale' to false, the sale is canceled

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

nftCarInfos.details: Mapping the NFT ID with the car informations

nftIdAndDelegator.details: Mapping the NFT ID with the delegator

nftIdAndOwner.details: Mapping the NFT ID with the owner
